<p class="ayah 11-59" id="59" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتِلْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَادٌ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) Aad,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَحَدُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they rejected</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) their Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَصَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and disobeyed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُسُلَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">His Messengers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱتَّبَعُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and followed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) command</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَبَّارٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">tyrant</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنِيدٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">obstinate.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"