<p class="ayah 11-61" id="61" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ وَإِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثَمُودَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thamud</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخَاهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(We sent) their brother</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَـٰلِحًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Salih.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰقَوْمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"O my people!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱعْبُدُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Worship</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you have</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَـٰهٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">god</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَيْرُهُۥ‌ۖ