tl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّاسُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the mankind,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّشْهُودٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">witnessed.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>103<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
