<p class="ayah 11-105" id="105" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(it) comes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكَلَّمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will speak</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِإِذْنِهِۦ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by His leave.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمِنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then among them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَقِىٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be the) wretched,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَسَعِيدٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (the) glad.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>105<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
