<p class="ayah 11-111" id="111" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلاًّ لَّمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to each [when]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَيُوَفِّيَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely will pay them in full</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْمَـٰلَهُمْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their deeds.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَبِيرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) All-Aware.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>111<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
